premise_source_doc_sentence: It is the band 's first studio album since 2010 's The Fall , and features collaborations from several artists including Vince Staples , Popcaan , D.R.A.M. , Grace Jones , Anthony Hamilton , De La Soul , Danny Brown , Kelela , Mavis Staples , Pusha T , and Benjamin Clementine .
His discography , as a solo artist , began in 2009 and includes three studio albums/extended plays , one collaboration album , three live albums and several other singles/featured singles .
